Package org.naregi.rns.client

RNS client APIs.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
RNSClient RNSClient object is generated by RNSClientHome.getRNSClient().
RNSExtensionClient RNSExtensionClient object is generated by RNSClientHome.getRNSExtensionClient().
RNSIterator<E> Iterator interface for List and Search operations.
RNSRecursiveListener Callback interface for recursive operations.
RNSSearchClient RNSSearchClient object is generated by RNSClientHome.getRNSSearchClient().
 

Class Summary
BaseClient Web service client APIs for Globus.
DirnameBasename Divided pathname into dirname and basename.
GlobusURLFixed Extend and modify org.globus.util.GlobusURL
GridFTPUtil Utilities for FTP and GridFTP client.
RNSAddHandle Handle for preparation of bulk Add operation.
RNSClientHome Interpret command options and Initialize RNS client environments.
RNSClientImpl RNSClient implementation.
RNSDirent Represent a RNS directory.
RNSDirentComparator Comparator for RNSDirent.
RNSDirHandle Handle to get an entry.
RNSExtensionClientImpl RNSExtensionClient implementation.
RNSKeyValue Key/Value operations to RNS Metadata.
RNSListIterator RNS list operation client to access WS-Iterator service.
RNSPortTypeCache Cache response data of RNS operations (Lookup, GetMultipleResourceProperties) (Directory cache).
RNSSearchClientImpl RNSSearchClientImpl implementation.
RNSSearchResult A result data structure of RNS search.
RNSSearchResultHandle Handle for results of Search operation.
RNSStat Structure for RNS directory properties.
